{"tid":2440955,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"劉鳴煒：有信心海洋公園撥款獲通過","createTime":"2021-03-10T10:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T10:55:35.000Z","uid":362414,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"beef2320544f1f3b7899fbaf00ec68ca5cedcece","tid":2440955,"uid":362414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:28:10.000Z","msg":"海洋公園主席劉鳴煒表示，公園重開後人流如預期，但在舊有的運作模式下，加上疫情，令財務受極大挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n劉鳴煒出席與保良局的合作計劃開幕禮後，表示海洋公園的未來發展方案，要繼續開源節流，希望在財委會得到支持和撥款。他說，得到撥款不是必然，要積極爭取各黨派立法會議員支持，過去數星期有官員和議員到公園視察 ，反應大部分正面，有信心會獲通過，暫時無其他後備方案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579821-20210310.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579821-20210310.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwpld3lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=cc8ca899\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579821-20210310.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=83d2db6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579821-20210310.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e37717163593225d5d89dd132cf7ad77ace4d99d","tid":2440955,"uid":331590,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:34:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算有泛民係到都照過嫁啦, on9仔up咩撚野"},{"pid":"ae49187f281dbc3a0648f74f8fe02e2cc1f23f13","tid":2440955,"uid":343712,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:35:30.000Z","msg":"唔怪得你老豆唔肯交盤生意你管，果然明智。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b26c1598008adde25923829f876d3d3d16f660a8","tid":2440955,"uid":245441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:35:47.000Z","msg":"是忠誠的"},{"pid":"a163ac023ea449a55e7fb4e67638c7ce3e76a370","tid":2440955,"uid":321374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:36:40.000Z","msg":"叫